    <h1>Geotagging Images</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of embedding GPS coordinates into an image's EXIF metadata so search engines, maps, and business profiles can associate the visual with a specific place. A quiet but compounding local SEO signal.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
