              <tr><td><strong>Facebook / Instagram</strong></td><td class="cell-no">No</td><td class="cell-meh">Low</td><td>Strips EXIF on upload; use platform geotag instead</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Website blog / location pages</strong></td><td class="cell-meh">Partial</td><td class="cell-meh">Low</td><td>Preserved if server doesn't re-encode</td></tr>
            </tbody>
